Key Match Events: Cade Povich struck out 10 while pitching into the eighth inning, and the Baltimore Orioles took a big early lead on their way to a 9-0 victory over the White Sox.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Orioles drubbed the White Sox again 9-0, sending Chicago to its 12th consecutive defeat, 109th loss
The game was played at Oriole Park at Camden Yards with an attendance of 15,108
The White Sox are 31-109 overall and 13-55 on the road
